"msg":"<blockquote>巴打我又係有上莊<br />\n又係得d hi bye friend<br />\n中學以前d friend又疏遠曬<br />\n你係咪我黎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只可以話為上莊付出左太多<br />\n到頭來冇野收獲到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1da22d2f043d9b2cf0cdb347ad7759c02530af77","tid":17341,"uid":43804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T23:41:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真心對人好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我好少打開晒個心咩都同人講<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最後都發覺自己響其他人心目中一文不值</blockquote><br />\n唉，自己對人真心，但人地就搵你笨柒，呢種感覺試得太多次之後，自己都唔想交個心出黎對人了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f078ea370057593237018a8c02eca0b8ca2a3fcf","tid":17341,"uid":41250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T23:43:44.000Z","msg":"岀泥做野更加冇啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a2b74fb101d1322904b831b2e3d84ce7132e692","tid":17341,"uid":26176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T23:44:32.000Z","msg":"你係咪有結識障礙？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cc7d682a6733e511b084f77fd7388e99ca13009","tid":17341,"uid":293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T23:47:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你係咪有結識障礙？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5128bc175b08b3d0a81e22c93888013fa2aa0a41","tid":17341,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T23:47:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你係咪有結識障礙？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n只要將問題變成病就再無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc4ffaa22275c8109ad8405e4903c873955fe50f","tid":17341,"uid":43978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T04:46:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你係咪有結識障礙？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有結識真心朋友障礙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有大量hi bye<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cadcce17886426290d77b4f0eb668f693b53b3c","tid":17341,"uid":11666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T04:49:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 加一 我有社交障礙同情緒病 唔識同人相處 自己一個人好冇安全感"},{"pid":"b3e81c669d9e0f3b8b2b15d00a17e834f68dcff8","tid":17341,"uid":20696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T04:54:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>成日扮social<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又無朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n日日戴住個面具做人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n心聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你扮到好social既時候大家就真係會當你係咁<br />\n1. 覺得你係social撚<br />\n2. 覺得你已經好多朋友<br />\n呢兩種人我只會同佢地係hi bye唔會想交心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n認同上面講你想搵可以交心既朋友就要先拎個心出黎<br />\n不過我覺得你首先要簡定一兩個對象先然後再深交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05db63539f387b80e6a24e475862719370c91036","tid":17341,"uid":2906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T05:03:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>真心對人好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我好少打開晒個心咩都同人講<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最後都發覺自己響其他人心目中一文不值</blockquote><br />\n唉，自己對人真心，但人地就搵你笨柒，呢種感覺試得太多次之後，自己都唔想交個心出黎對人了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nExactly...我每次識都攞個心出嚟 但唔係個個都咁對返你...開始對啲人無乜期望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31f498de2ab0c96868c69208ce1d281677eb3c7a","tid":17341,"uid":22826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T05:08:14.000Z","msg":"揀返d唔太mk既人做朋友"},{"pid":"5d71c97f583db2b56c78723f0c41bbc3b5afd737","tid":17341,"uid":36786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T05:18:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都無朋友"},{"pid":"4b0319c2bc89a52b33f36de406848d7d164835bb","tid":17341,"uid":29645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T13:44:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都無朋友</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都係"},{"pid":"5c9580e12264664b27a4cc046693bbd24079ea71","tid":17341,"uid":8750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T13:47:34.000Z","msg":"我明啊 身同感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\"